column2: you can drag modules into different slots. If you hold CTRL while dragging, the module will be copied instead of moved.
By pressing ALT you can freeze the UI, so you can move your mouse freely around.
Legacy modules can be stored for later reuse with the button that will be visible above the module specs. Legacy modules can be managed under Settings.
Live mode will autoconfigure the settings to match the current state in-game. This only works for the current ship.
Module changes can be tracked. If a module is set as equipped, it will be colored in yellow. Any changes will turn the color to blue. These changes are considered when creating a wishlist.
